    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div id="outline-container-1" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="sec-1">project euler problem 1</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-1">


</div>

<div id="outline-container-1-1" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="sec-1-1">Problem</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-1-1">

<blockquote>

<p>If we list all the natural numbers below 10 that are multiples of 3 or 5, we get 3, 5, 6 and 9. The sum of these multiples is 23.
</p>
<p>
Find the sum of all the multiples of 3 or 5 below 1000.
</p>
</blockquote>


</div>

</div>

<div id="outline-container-1-2" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="sec-1-2">Solution</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-1-2">

<p>   可以直接遍历找出所有整除3或5的数，然后相加，需要O(n)。但如果运用数学集合的概念,只要O(1).
</p>
<p>
   基本思路:
</p>
<ol>
<li>所有被3整除数相加
        3 + 6 + &hellip; + 999 = 3 * (1 + 2 + &hellip; + 333)
</li>
<li>加上所有被5整除数
        5 + 10 + &hellip; + 995 = 5 * (1 + 2 + &hellip; + 199)
</li>
<li>减去被15整除的数
        15 + 30 + &hellip; + 995 = 15 * (1 + 2 + &hellip;+ 16)
</li>
</ol>



<p>
   其中(1 + 2 + &hellip; + n) = (1 + n) * n / 2;
</p>
<p>
   333 = floor(1000/3);
</p>
</div>

</div>

<div id="outline-container-1-3" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="sec-1-3">Answer</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-1-3">

<p>  233168
</p>
<p>
